{"word":"ἐκλέγω","slug":"ἐκλέγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰλέγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λέγω\">λέγω</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκλεκτός\">ἐκλεκτός</a></el> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λόγος\">λόγος</a></el>; ‘pick, single out’] in our <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ lit.\">lit.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> only<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘pick out for oneself’, <b>choose, select <a href='B:480 13:20'>Mk 13:20</a>; <a href='B:490 10:42'>Lk 10:42</a>; <a href='B:490 14:7'>14:7</a>; <a href='B:500 6:70'>J 6:70</a>; <a href='B:500 15:16'>15:16</a>; <a href='B:510 1:2'>Ac 1:2</a>; <a href='B:530 1:27'>1 Cor 1:27</a>; <a href='B:660 2:5'>Js 2:5</a>;</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to a decision involving choice of persons <b><a href='B:510 15:7'>Ac 15:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> In <b><a href='B:490 6:44'>Lk 6:44</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>,</b> <el>ἐ.</el> (for <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:συλλέγω\">συλλέγω</a></el>) focuses on the harvest of selected items <b>pick from.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔκλαυσα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκλείπω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}